---
const CHANNEL = 'https://www.youtube.com/@YTILIKAN';
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<section class="contact" id="contact">
  <svg class="contact__pattern" aria-hidden="true"><rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="url(#maskpat)"/></svg>
  <div class="wrap contact__inner">
    <svg class="mark contact__mark reveal" viewBox="0 0 200 200"><use href="#ytmark"/></svg>
    <h2 class="contact__title reveal" data-delay="80">
      Construisons une Afrique qui comprend<br />
      la technologie — <em>parce qu'on y participe.</em>
    </h2>
    <p class="contact__lead reveal" data-delay="160">
      Rejoignez la communauté Y'TILIKAN. Curieux, étudiant, professionnel,
      intervenant ou partenaire — il y a une place pour vous.
    </p>
    <div class="contact__cta reveal" data-delay="240">
      <a href={CHANNEL} target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="cbtn cbtn--gold">Suivre sur YouTube</a>
      <a href="mailto:contact@ytilikan.com" class="cbtn cbtn--ghost">Nous écrire</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<footer class="foot">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="foot__lock">
      <svg class="mark foot__mark" viewBox="0 0 200 200"><use href="#ytmark"/></svg>
      <span class="foot__wm">Y'TILIKAN</span>
    </div>
    <p class="foot__desc">Une communauté de partage qui vulgarise l'IA pour l'Afrique et sa diaspora. Ensemble, construisons une Afrique où l'on comprend la technologie — parce qu'on y participe pleinement.</p>
    <div class="foot__row">
      <span class="foot__meta">© {year} Y'TILIKAN · Tous droits réservés</span>
      <span class="foot__meta foot__meta--gold">Ce n'est pas sorcier.</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>

<style>
  .contact {
    background: var(--indigo);
    color: var(--ivoire);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    padding: 110px 0;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .contact__pattern { position: absolute; inset: 0; opacity: .08; pointer-events: none; }
  .contact__inner { position: relative; z-index: 2; max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .contact__mark { width: 76px; height: 76px; color: var(--ocre); margin: 0 auto 28px; }
  .contact__title {
    font-family: var(--display); font-weight: 800;
    font-size: clamp(1.9rem, 4.4vw, 3rem);
    letter-spacing: -.02em; line-height: 1.05; margin-bottom: 22px;
  }
  .contact__title em { font-style: normal; color: var(--ocre); }
  .contact__lead { font-size: 1.12rem; color: #d9d2c4; max-width: 56ch; margin: 0 auto 38px; }
  .contact__cta { display: flex; gap: 14px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .cbtn {
    font-family: var(--display); font-weight: 700; font-size: .95rem;
    padding: 13px 26px; border-radius: 40px;
    transition: transform .2s, background .2s, border-color .2s, color .2s;
  }
  .cbtn--gold { background: var(--ocre); color: var(--encre); }
  .cbtn--gold:hover { background: var(--ocre-d); transform: translateY(-2px); }
  .cbtn--ghost { border: 1.5px solid #ffffff33; color: var(--ivoire); }
  .cbtn--ghost:hover { border-color: var(--ocre); color: var(--ocre); }

  .foot { background: var(--encre); color: var(--ivoire); padding: 70px 0; }
  .foot__lock { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 18px; margin-bottom: 22px; }
  .foot__mark { width: 52px; height: 52px; color: var(--ocre); }
  .foot__wm { font-family: var(--display); font-weight: 800; font-size: 1.7rem; }
  .foot__desc { color: #a9a294; max-width: 52ch; font-size: .98rem; }
  .foot__row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-end; gap: 30px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 40px; }
  .foot__meta { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: .72rem; letter-spacing: .1em; color: #7d7568; text-transform: uppercase; }
  .foot__meta--gold { color: var(--ocre); }
</style>
